title: Octopus Underwater
description: An octopus swimming gracefully underwater, showcasing its long tentacles and distinctive suckers. The background features a gradient of blue-green water, creating a serene marine environment.

title: Acorn on Oak Tree

title: Thylacine and Tasmanian Tiger

title: Cormorant Drying Its Wings
description: A cormorant stands on a small mound in the water, with its wings spread wide open. The bird has a sleek black plumage, and its yellow-orange beak contrasts with its dark feathers. The background is blurred, suggesting a natural habitat, likely a wetland or lake.
